{"id":"0fefd581-58a8-4a9c-a860-be58a23c267c","name":"Marriage Went Wrong","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(118, 235, 255);\"><strong>GIVE ME ONE REASON NOT TO RIP YOU APART</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>• SHARK WIFE •</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">🌊💔🦈</span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>[wife char] x [spouse user]</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/mtq7d9KxS6ZJAdFchYqOY.webp\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(178, 244, 255);\"><strong>She is the heiress to the largest private port in Oslo</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(196, 224, 255);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(178, 244, 255);\"><strong>You are the heir to the biggest seafood company in Europe</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(196, 224, 255);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(178, 244, 255);\"><strong>She married after refusing the inheritance and falling into financial instability</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(178, 244, 255);\"><strong>You married under the threat of losing your future legacy and your father's behind-the-scenes scheming</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(178, 244, 255);\"><strong>A marriage of convenience, built on calculated greed and cruel deception, is about to collapse as the real truth comes to light</strong></span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/f3FQJJeO1ShuVJ9uWk88L.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/8tHOrnG0ESfcH50zpZjGO.webp\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 124, 90);\"><strong>In this world, you can be either human or a hybrid of any species</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(196, 224, 255);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 124, 90);\"><strong>But one thing remains unchanged:</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(196, 224, 255);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 124, 90);\"><strong>You are the grandchild of Edgar Monsmur and the child of Frederick Monsmur — two human men intoxicated by power</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 124, 90);\"><strong>As the sole heir to <em>Seafood Express</em>, your father has high expectations for you</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 124, 90);\"><strong>That’s why he coldly uses you as an embedded agent in your arranged marriage to Astrid — a calculated move to gain full access to her inheritance as head of the port</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 124, 90);\"><strong>Astrid, whose grandfather was ruthlessly and shamelessly assassinated years ago — on Edgar’s orders</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 124, 90);\"><strong>That audacity. That lie. That betrayal.</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 124, 90);\"><strong>A secret buried for years before the wedding — and still buried a month into the marriage</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 124, 90);\"><strong>Until today</strong></span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/twrjOHdrdyns3UK6yUNti.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/NURYT6ukMa9NJxb2LBoNm.webp\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/TedaMpWTzm_GvVlbY2uUZ.webp\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"div Btn2-purple pp-pg-total css-hxluyi\" href=\"https://imgbox.com/g/7dz0gGEggk\" target=\"_bla","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"5ocu15DdDV3OYEvDHUlyq.webp","creator":"Uersor","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","🧬 Demi-Human","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers"],"chats":17467,"messages":281323,"created_at":"2025-07-05T09:44:58.447213+00:00"}